<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="vi">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Audio Guide Admin - Login</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            min-height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
            background:
                radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(255,255,255,.18), transparent 32%),
                linear-gradient(135deg, #0f1f31, #17324d 45%, #c97732 100%);
            font-family: "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
        }

        .auth-shell {
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 32px 16px;
        }

        .auth-panel {
            width: min(960px, 100%);
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1.1fr .9fr;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,.96);
            border-radius: 28px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 28px 64px rgba(7, 16, 29, .28);
        }

        .auth-hero {
            padding: 48px;
            color: #fff;
            background:
                linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(10, 24, 39, .15), rgba(10, 24, 39, .35)),
                url("https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1504674900247-0877df9cc836?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1200&q=80") center/cover;
        }

        .auth-hero h1 {
            font-size: clamp(2rem, 3vw, 3rem);
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }

        .auth-hero p {
            font-size: 1rem;
            line-height: 1.7;
            max-width: 420px;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .auth-card {
            padding: 40px 36px;
            background: #f9fbff;
        }

        .auth-card .card {
            border: 0;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 18px 40px rgba(14, 31, 53, .08);
        }

        .form-control {
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 12px 14px;
        }

        .btn {
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 12px 16px;
        }

        @@media (max-width: 900px) {
            .auth-panel {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }

            .auth-hero {
                min-height: 220px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="auth-shell">
        <div class="auth-panel">
            <section class="auth-hero">
                <span class="badge text-bg-light mb-3">Audio Tour Admin</span>
                <h1>Quản trị hệ thống thuyết minh đa ngôn ngữ</h1>
                <p>Đăng nhập để quản lý POI, TTS script, bản dịch, tour và theo dõi dữ liệu sử dụng của phố ẩm thực Vĩnh Khánh.</p>
            </section>
            <section class="auth-card">
                @RenderBody()
            </section>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
